"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"随着以太坊名称服务（$ENS）和 Paraswap（$PSP）最近进行代币空投，一些人可能已经开始主动寻找下一次空投。\\n\\n明确，空投农业是一种活动，很可能是非常投机的行为，有什么办法可以确定成功的因素。最终是否会进行投，即使他们破坏了哪些行为有资格进行空投。\\n\\n[Paraswap 最近的空投](https://www.coindesk.com/tech/2021/11/15/dex-aggregator-paraswap-launches-psp-token-on-heels-of-ens-airdrop-excitement/)通知疏远了许多真实用户，因为他们从各自协议交互的 100 万多个地址中识别并过滤掉了 20,000 名合法用户。\\n\\n巴特，我们认为还有可能并尝试一下这些应用程序和协议，不管它们最终是否会进行空投，事实上，有一些可能是您已经在使用的。\\n\\n在本文中，我们将探索 8 个值得关注的有前景的空投。\\n\\n# #1 — 元掩码\\n\\n[Metamask](https://metamask.io/)是一个内置交换功能的强大功能。用户可以通过应用程序购买、存储、发送和交换代币。作为生命世界的入口，您可以连接到各种区块链、与 dApp 交互、管理您的健康等等。\\n\\n**为什么我们**觉得会被**空投：** Metamask全球用户使用。Coin98和Trust Wallet等其他钱包过去也推出过代币。\\n\\n**如何潜在地进行空投：**在支持的链上使用 Metamask 中的交换功能。请注意，Metamask 掉期收取 0.8% 的费用。\\n\\n# #2 — Opensea\\n\\n[Opensea](https://opensea.io/) is one of the biggest trading avenues for buying and selling non fungible tokens, or NFTs. We [previously described](https://medium.com/stakingbits/how-to-buy-nfts-from-opensea-689b7c4e5f39) how you can potentially use Opensea to buy and sell NFTs.\\n\\n**Why we think there will be an airdrop:** Other NFT marketplaces like Rarible have a token. Investors in Opensea would look to exit in future and we think an airdrop makes the most sense for Web 3.0 dApps.\\n\\n**How to potentially farm the airdrop:** Buy and sell NFTs on Opensea, on all the blockchains that they are in. We think that the airdrop would be determined by volume traded and whether you’re a buyer, seller or both.\\n\\n# #3 — Rabbithole\\n\\n[Rabbithole](https://rabbithole.gg/) allows users to earn crypto by becoming an early adopter of new projects and earn crypto as a reward. For projects, they can attract new users and stakeholders and distribute tokens through proof-of-use.\\n\\n**Why we think there will be an airdrop:** We think that Rabbithole is plugged deeply in the DeFi space and will eventually reward its users and early adopters.\\n\\n**How to potentially farm the airdrop:** Complete a few quests on Rabbithole and level up some skills. We think that your EXP level in Rabbithole would have an impact on the amount of airdrop received.\\n\\n# #4 — Zapper\\n\\n[Zapper](https://zapper.fi/) is a dApp for DeFi portfolio management to manage your DeFi portfolios from a single place, including tracking of assets and debt, investing directly into liquidity pools and savings platforms. It supports multiple blockchains and hundreds of protocols so you don’t have to navigate multiple apps to track your positions.\\n\\n**Why we think there will be an airdrop:** They launched gamification features, quests and NFTs. While they have no plans to do an airdrop in the short term, they do have plans to incentivize the building and maintaining of a front-end application with a new token model in future.\\n\\n**How to potentially farm the airdrop:** Use the app, connect your wallet, swap, pool and invest using their app, across multiple blockchains if possible. Accumulate EXP and redeem NFTs.\\n\\n# #5 — DeFiSaver\\n\\nDeFiSaver 是允许一个备用板，用于创建、管理和跟踪您的 DeFi 头寸。某些操作例如，自动用户恢复某些 LTV 的。DeFiSaver 为任何人介绍了自创定义 DeFi 配方的方法，你可以在其中构建自己的自定义模板。\\n\\n**因为我们认为**会有更多的**空投：**大量用户，而优质的产品。FuruCombo 专属的 DeFiSaver，也推出了代币。\\n\\n**如何潜在地进行空投：**使用该程序并使用它运行自动化。\\n\\n# ＃6 - Sablier财务\\n\\n[Sablier Finance](https://app.sablier.finance/)是一个实时支付平台，发件人可以在其中将付款从一方实时传输到另一方。\\n\\n**我们为什么认为**会有**空投：** Sablier为许多协议的DAO和投资者提供了支持。\\n\\n**如何潜在地进行空投：**创造金钱流着一条银子流向生活\\n\\n# #7 — 跳协议\\n\\n[Hop 协议](https://hop.exchange/)为 Hop Exchange 提供动力——可扩展的汇总到汇总通用令牌桥。它允许用户几乎立即将令牌从一个汇总发送到另一个汇总，而无需等待汇总的质询期。\\n\\n**为什么我们认为会有空投：**其他跨链桥通过代币来鼓励流动性（例如$SYN）。\\n\\n基本**地进行空投：**在多少并架设代币，为合欢的流动性池提供流动注注性质\\n\\n# #8超流体\\n\\nSuperfluid 是一种用于高温的协议，允许用户通过立即开始、无固定终止日期、流量、完全喷射无将流向生命。\\n\\n与 Sablier 不同的语言在您的流时不会锁定您的当前状态。\\n\\n**因为我们认为**会有**空投：**与 Sab 类似，我们认为 Superfluid 可能会在未来推出代币，因为更多的协议和 DAO 需要更好的基础设施来支持付费贡献者。\\n\\n潜在**地进行空投：如何**使用超流向其他人流钱。\\n\\n代币空投确实是一份礼物，如果幸运的话，它们可能会改变生活。例如，我们在两个高峰期都可以获得价值 30,000 美元的 UNI 空投和价值 40,000 美元的 $ENS 空投！如果您正在寻找这文章未满的其他可能空投，请查看[此日志](https://medium.com/stakingbits/identify-potential-airdrops-with-defillamas-airdrop-page-e969bc4ca03e)。\",\"timestamp\":1639916896,\"title\":\"Top 8 potential airdrops to look out for\"},\"digest\":\"kNMDF9EVQf4Dl5TTOXR33stECvDKpUcgxtwPjUN2npA\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xE18000D69D78BbE80B3a5ceCCA512A78012Cbf4f\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"2aeW86Ur3fyOnkugcvC_vW6T1OWeh3gPNFTO3ZOOAKE\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"ynLXAtaHnXlgBePsMwKEp3XaVOpBWoSFDDEWtPDtk6g\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"SSOmHsn2FwYjiSlZq0bkjHuO9E5I9IWkFZy0R3zsEx5qgn9p86_vEPS1rZcVVGqufb_8vgnzNzqLl9NaS650Ng\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x156c8b221ce46abc4f0dac2d144f8ca8b1c69d599d461b882809e39a6d9626937133921d88204190084a9b3dbfd18d9df895d4a001145555362e846e3fe332ee1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"2aeW86Ur3fyOnkugcvC_vW6T1OWeh3gPNFTO3ZOOAKE\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"ynLXAtaHnXlgBePsMwKEp3XaVOpBWoSFDDEWtPDtk6g\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"kNMDF9EVQf4Dl5TTOXR33stECvDKpUcgxtwPjUN2npA\"}"